game.description:
Are you a jigsaw puzzle lover? If you are, you should definitely try out your hand in this brand new arcade challenge where fun level will be on the different level. Swan Puzzle Challenge can be an ultimate treat for all jigsaw puzzle challenge lovers. Gamers from all age groups can try it out their preferred devices ? be it a computer, mobile phone or tablet. Your objective in this free online puzzle game is to collect all the pieces and complete the picture.?

Solving out all the puzzles of this free online game will help keep your brain sharp and improve your brain memory. Easy, medium and hard ? there are three different modes to choose from. Choose anyone of them and get ready to challenge your memory! In easy mode, you will have only a few pieces to connect. The number of picture pieces will increase as soon as the level increases in this cool HTML5 game. Get a chance to have a leisurely gaming experience to complete the level!

You can use your mouse or tap to play this one of the best platform games for kids. On your mobile phone or tablet, you can swipe or tap the screen. Complete all the 12 levels with a focused mind and sharp brain! Practice the needful cognitive skills to help yourself become the champion of a puzzle!
